Setup generation of open api spec json Using swashbuckle
dotnet add package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore.Swagger dotnet tool install --global Swashbuckle.AspNetCore.Cli dotnet build Generate openAPI spec dotnet build swagger tofile --output &#34;openapi.json&#34; bin/Debug/net8.0/bkr-provider-api.dll [version] # e.g swagger tofile --output &#34;openapi.json&#34; bin/Debug/net8.0/bkr-provider-api.dll v1 OpenAPI diff https://github.com/OpenAPITools/openapi-diff Compare two openAPI specs to find breaking changes in the contract. openapi-diff &lt;old&gt; &lt;new&gt;
# two openapi specs from files docker run --rm -v ${PWD}:/spec openapitools/openapi-diff /spec/openapi_v4.json /spec/openapi_v5.json # spec from url.

